{"tid":938052,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"探事頭婆兼自駕遊（回帶整理中）🇬🇧","createTime":"2018-12-12T03:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T22:50:43.000Z","uid":144369,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"903ea2c6cf663815f63a9aacc01555785966f0be","tid":938052,"uid":144369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T03:56:14.000Z","msg":"大家好，係香港長大左幾十年，終於有機會係十月初探一探事頭婆，作為經歷過殖民統治嘅本土香港人，更加嚮往英國之旅。<br />\n此趟旅行算係與太太嘅蜜月之旅，為期十日左右。<br />\n希望係呢個post同大家分享下點滴同埋自駕遊。<br />\n小弟為人好隨性，好多行程都會視乎情況作臨時更改，所以不會走馬燈咁睇好多唔同嘅地方，所以去嘅地方未必如預期般好多。<br />\n相信呢度好多巴打絲打而家或曾經係英國生活過，大家比我更熟悉英國，希望有錯指正，無錯大家交流分享🙋🏾&zwj;♂️<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ajyD7n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ajyD7n.png&h=f738e048&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/32enxsp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F32enxsp.png&h=aa028807&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z8PKLNq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz8PKLNq.png&h=763f8148&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k56ts0M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk56ts0M.png&h=c5a8cdde&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmdfSst.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmdfSst.png&h=e276f52b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U0znxsv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU0znxsv.png&h=06a282d9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ap9F3zb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fap9F3zb.png&h=40ffa692&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X5eCmkU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX5eCmkU.png&h=3e953ebc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《行程》<br />\n<br />\n此趟行程大概十日左右<br />\n<br />\nDay 1-3<br />\n香港-》倫敦（LHR)<br />\n倫敦市內觀光<br />\n<br />\nDay 4 (自駕遊開始）<br />\nLondon &mdash;&gt; Oxford （60miles)<br />\nBicester Village<br />\nOxford town<br />\n<br />\nDay 5<br />\nOxford &mdash;&gt; Westonbirt Arboretum &mdash;&gt;Bath (80miles)<br />\nWestonbirt Arboretum 睇紅葉🍁<br />\nBath Town Visit<br />\n<br />\nDay 6<br />\nBath &mdash;&gt; Castle Combe &mdash;&gt; Burton-on-the-water (50Miles)<br />\nBurton-on-the-water &mdash;&gt; York (180Miles)<br />\n<br />\nDay 7<br />\nYork Town Visit<br />\nYork &mdash;&gt; Manchester (75 miles)<br />\n還車🚗<br />\n<br />\nDay 8<br />\nManchester City Visit<br />\n<br />\nDay 9<br />\nLiverpool city visit ( Train)<br />\n<br />\nDay 10<br />\nManchester &mdash;&gt; HKG😭<br />\n<br />\n其實因為大部份時間自駕，所以時間過得好快<br />\n亦感覺很充實。<br />\n<br />\n慢慢會係下面同各位分享一下。<br />\n請多多指教🙇🏾&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"fefb8ed904a3e6881f4f260e18e97f767ac358b1","tid":938052,"uid":144369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:17:42.000Z","msg":"《交通安排》<br />\n<br />\n倫敦交通個人觀感在市中心其實幾方便，相對很多外國嘅大城市例如LA,Amsterdam，倫敦地鐵網已經算方便，覆蓋大部份景點，此行小弟只係去左幾個想去嘅地方，基本地鐵都已經可以到達。<br />\n當然部份倫敦嘅鐵路係冇冷氣，天熱如果隔離有個大汗嘅肥哥哥，應該會係賞心樂事。<br />\n<br />\n建議大家去倫敦嘅時候出一張oyster卡，此卡有如香港嘅八達通一樣，出入會比較方便，又唔需要成日去買車飛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NxUOJj7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNxUOJj7.png&h=6c43b75c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於倫敦以外地方，小弟今次去幾個城市例如牛津， 利物浦等都有完善嘅巴士網絡，曼市更有輕鐵系統，大家都可以一試。<br />\n<br />\n不過如果好似小弟咁橫跨幾個唔同嘅城市，建議自駕，因為去郊區就會好唔方便，而且英國嘅鐵路票格比較貴，城市之間嘅火車票價閒閒地都要10磅以上，而且英國營運嘅火車公司都有不同，有好多唔同嘅選擇，如果即日來回，會建議買來回票，因為比較化算。<br />\n<br />\n例如由曼市去利物浦，小弟去單程票價13磅，來回係14.3磅，即係俾多13蚊港紙可以回程，買飛嘅時候要多加留意。<br />\n<br />\n同樣情況係通用係巴士同輕鐵身上，來回票價會比單程便宜很多，大家上車前要小心留意，可以慳番唔小。😌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KB6Ymcv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKB6Ymcv.png&h=285c8ec9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7JqY5Ed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7JqY5Ed.png&h=93882a70&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P6j3xjh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP6j3xjh.png&h=f4849985&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ZS1iZk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ZS1iZk.png&h=552eedba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然，英國都有的士服務，不過小弟真心覺得比較貴，如非必要，都係考慮坐其他交通工具或且Uber , 小弟只係曼市坐過一次Uber去機場，價錢都叫合理，大家可以上網比較價錢先。<br />\n<br />\n待續"},{"pid":"9b0aef7804ab45d12f08acf3057255e92b7357b0","tid":938052,"uid":2927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T04:07:54.000Z","msg":"正呀屌 黎緊大假就係想咁玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e18d9f1f708df86a31917dd4889bccccb22aaa32","tid":938052,"uid":144369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b0aef7804ab45d12f08acf3057255e92b7357b0","tid":938052,"uid":2927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T04:07:54.000Z","msg":"正呀屌 黎緊大假就係想咁玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T04:14:23.000Z","msg":"巴打（絲打）會去幾多日？<br />\n我去左九日都好似唔夠咁🤤<br />\n<br />\n會去咩地方，如果有問題我識答嘅可以互相交流下"},{"pid":"77c2390b4a59ec031d0bc2f3c7b447dd128ae15d","tid":938052,"uid":3273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T04:16:32.000Z","msg":"揸咩車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93bee9adb565eaea4d843d7fe653e6b8f0324351","tid":938052,"uid":144369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"77c2390b4a59ec031d0bc2f3c7b447dd128ae15d","tid":938052,"uid":3273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T04:16:32.000Z","msg":"揸咩車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T05:28:31.000Z","msg":"租車公司俾左架Volvo V40我<br />\n好新淨，開左1000公里左右<br />\n不過嫌佢1.6唔係好夠力😆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EThD6LD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEThD6LD.png&h=9c59c65d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後會分享多少少自駕趣事（柒事）😆"},{"pid":"74c0865cb64d41fd9c4c28fc5469653316606554","tid":938052,"uid":144369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T09:38:21.000Z","msg":"《洛丁山及海德》<br />\n<br />\n係倫敦，個人有五件想做嘅，今次有幸可以做到其中三件（大家唔好見笑，鄉下仔難得出城，所謂成就解鎖亦唔係咩大事，純個人喜好）<br />\n<br />\n其中兩件就係去Nottinghill 同埋海德公園。<br />\n亦係今次小弟係倫敦一定要做嘅事（太太白眼中🙄）<br />\n<br />\n洛丁山<br />\n<br />\n作為曾經大口珠嘅Fans，Nottinghill 一定係不能忘記嘅作品，一落機便抽空去左呢個地方，去會一會果一間書店，睇一睇果一堆七彩嘅建築物，算係解鎖一個成就。<br />\n呢個地方亦會有街頭市集，大家可以買下紀念品或且新鮮嘅蔬菜水果。未去過倫敦嘅朋友，絕對推介。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rLdG5QP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrLdG5QP.png&h=6ee757ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3M3TcvR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3M3TcvR.png&h=008f97b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GN743Cy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGN743Cy.png&h=64fa17bb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y03ozKf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy03ozKf.png&h=60d0ba51&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4ghEaX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4ghEaX.png&h=a84f34f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z0tcs4j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0tcs4j.png&h=d6f061b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海德公園<br />\n<br />\n小弟好鐘意行公園，果種藍天白雲生機處處嘅感覺。<br />\n可惜香港寸金尺土，搵一個行到腳軟可以hea足一日嘅地方唔多，所以好喜歡海德公園嘅寧靜，呆坐一日，同松鼠傾計，係行景點外嘅另類選擇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mwPGmtw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmwPGmtw.png&h=3848ea98&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2bn8LVd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2bn8LVd.png&h=8e913716&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L0rYoGU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL0rYoGU.png&h=084d076e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7U0qN8C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7U0qN8C.png&h=6b90fd30&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zww5N8F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZww5N8F.png&h=e91fc68a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n待續"},{"pid":"2c147050654c80e4e1ad8e1be54902ee10db8a93","tid":938052,"uid":3273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93bee9adb565eaea4d843d7fe653e6b8f0324351","tid":938052,"uid":144369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"77c2390b4a59ec031d0bc2f3c7b447dd128ae15d","tid":938052,"uid":3273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T04:16:32.000Z","msg":"揸咩車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T05:28:31.000Z","msg":"租車公司俾左架Volvo V40我<br />\n好新淨，開左1000公里左右<br />\n不過嫌佢1.6唔係好夠力😆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EThD6LD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEThD6LD.png&h=9c59c65d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後會分享多少少自駕趣事（柒事）😆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T13:04:19.000Z","msg":"Total 幾錢？？"},{"pid":"66f27dd113a01b7d56c71445641e195063652a13","tid":938052,"uid":144369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c147050654c80e4e1ad8e1be54902ee10db8a93","tid":938052,"uid":3273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93bee9adb565eaea4d843d7fe653e6b8f0324351","tid":938052,"uid":144369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"77c2390b4a59ec031d0bc2f3c7b447dd128ae15d","tid":938052,"uid":3273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T04:16:32.000Z","msg":"揸咩車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T05:28:31.000Z","msg":"租車公司俾左架Volvo V40我<b