未必好多嘅巴打絲打，英國會係日本之外一個唔錯嘅地方。 <br />\n<br />\n1）首先英國同香港一樣都係右駄駕駛，起碼唔需要從新適應出入路口嘅煩惱。<br />\n2）英國人開車比香港人相對禮讓，即使小路出大路都會一架一架讓，亦唔係好似香港咁開慢少少都俾人推車仔🙄<br />\n3）如果自駕，行李會比較容易安排。<br />\n<br />\n係選擇自駕遊之前，有幾件事要預算清楚。避免搞錯而失預算。<br />\n1）首先要大概諗好自己想去嘅景點，路線，同埋大概需要租車嘅日數。亦要大概諗好取車及還車嘅時間。當然英國大公司租車嘅地方都好方便，小弟為倫敦租車，曼市還車，兩者都係離酒店步行不足10分鐘嘅距離。<br />\n2）如果平日朝七晚八左右倫敦出或入，基本都需要付入城費（Congestion Charge)，呢個費用唔會包含係租車價入面。價錢為11.25磅，如果係呢個時間出入倫敦需要注意。基本租車公司可以代收或去便利店找付。大家有興趣可以參考以下<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tfl.gov.uk/modes/driving/congestion-charge/congestion-charge-zone\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftfl.gov.uk%2Fmodes%2Fdriving%2Fcongestion-charge%2Fcongestion-charge-zone&d=cGeTo8mfJM0e0XC%2FG8%2BgJzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=fca86498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tfl.gov.uk/modes/driving/congestion-charge/congestion-charge-zone</a><br />\n<br />\n3）租車要選好自己嘅選項，例如棍波定自動波等。小弟選擇左自動波，所以會比較貴少少。<br />\n<br />\n費用：<br />\n以小弟為例，小弟租車四日，倫敦拎車曼市還車，選擇四人自動波私家車，租車大概420磅再加油錢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pwKrHvp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpwKrHvp.png&h=40f0e108&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yfwURoL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyfwURoL.png&h=db3e23ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以小弟嘅經驗，請大家取車前一定要問清楚以下資料<br />\n<br />\n1）還車時需要滿油還車抑或是如何，收費亦如何<br />\n（其實H字頭租車係提供兩個嘅選擇，不過平衡計算，小弟決定滿油還車)<br />\n<br />\n2) 此車係汽油（petroleum)抑或柴油（Diesel)<br />\n呢一個係小弟親身嘅故事，請大家要問清楚。<br />\n*不過係英國，如果用汽油車，柴油槍係不能入到嘅，小弟親身試過🤭<br />\n<br />\n3）按金收費<br />\n<br />\n4）請檢查清楚車嘅狀況，有沒有撞花等等<br />\n不過H租車公司係我取車第一晚便詳細E貓左資料說明車身邊度花左。<br />\n<br />\n拎車，出發，下章分享開車同埋泊車嘅經驗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8DkKubo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8DkKubo.png&h=0a0f1e3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n待續"},{"pid":"ebfa38d827a71c54b7bdae39864cb083c468718c","tid":938052,"uid":91638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T07:21:00.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n<br />\n但調返轉汽油槍係入到柴油車到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5548159983f2b65dce03e7e5439c219c577d8363","tid":938052,"uid":144369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebfa38d827a71c54b7bdae39864cb083c468718c","tid":938052,"uid":91638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T07:21:00.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n<br />\n但調返轉汽油槍係入到柴油車到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T07:59:02.000Z","msg":"其實我試過係Shell同BP都係咁，汽油槍入唔到柴油車，柴油槍入唔到汽油車，其實諗到都驚險，所以租車前要問清楚🤧有時車俾嘅menu係冇架🤦🏾&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"74d265015a9897528c8349b8d8a417364f2cc3ba","tid":938052,"uid":178317,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T10:42:15.000Z","msg":"有update未,想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1dcab8e1b4f0b8216641699ebe70278db3b948","tid":938052,"uid":19310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T11:50:31.000Z","msg":"巴打加油，你快啲出完到我寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf775278667d83630b54d95e3f12a5d311d07434","tid":938052,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T11:55:47.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"1f2e9b9b9eaf485712b8aba371337220edb431a7","tid":938052,"uid":144369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74d265015a9897528c8349b8d8a417364f2cc3ba","tid":938052,"uid":178317,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T10:42:15.000Z","msg":"有update未,想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T12:10:03.000Z","msg":"寫左一半冇左，寫緊😭"},{"pid":"26dcc51550473d1250545974a6e87a5938cec651","tid":938052,"uid":144369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da1dcab8e1b4f0b8216641699ebe70278db3b948","tid":938052,"uid":19310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T11:50:31.000Z","msg":"巴打加油，你快啲出完到我寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T12:10:32.000Z","msg":"加油，大家寫互相交流🙋🏾&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"603a29148e73e8f4a0049b46fcf9818010fad952","tid":938052,"uid":144369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T13:16:27.000Z","msg":"《自駕 二》<br />\n<br />\n上回講到租車前嘅準備或一d我地要安排嘅事。<br />\n今日分享嘅主要係幾個今次自駕嘅分享，心得唔敢講，但係經驗嘅交流，大家有意見隨便問或交流。<br />\n<br />\n首先，每一個去英國開車嘅朋友都會同意，英國有好多迴旋處，係一條大概50Miles嘅路，可以有最少30-50個迴旋處不等， 小弟有一日由巴斯（Bath)開去約克，大概250英里嘅路，最少開左150-200個迴旋處，對於係香港開慣車嘅朋友，係別有一番體驗。<br />\n<br />\n不過英國開迴旋處要特別小心，有兩個點要提醒<br />\n1）右方來嘅車永遠優先，如果右方有車過來，要讓對方先過先可以出。<br />\n2）如果會喺迴旋處第一個路口出，請靠左行駛，如果會在迴旋處第二或第三或第四嘅出口，請不要做內線L，盡量靠右線駛出，如果做內線L好容易會有碰撞。<br />\n<br />\n英國開車單位係Miles(英里)而唔係KM（公里）,一公里大概係0.62英里，所以請留意<br />\n<br />\n第三，英國係高速公路及普通公路都有時速限制，由70到30不等，所以要小心。部份租車公司嘅GPS會提供相機提示，不過都係小心為上，有朋友曾經因爲開快車而俾法庭出傳票。<br />\n<br />\n第四，大家準備好景點時，最好先準備好postal code<br />\n這樣會比較方便輸入，例如要去約克嘅Betty&rsquo;s cafe, postal code 為YO1 8QP，呢一組號碼一如該地方嘅身份證，所以記住先安排好。<br />\n<br />\n第五，高速公路中間都會有好多休息站，大家可以休息下，切勿疲勞駕駛。<br />\n<br />\n第六，英國入油要自助，如我上文大家要留意自己車係柴油（diesel)定係汽油（petroleum)。 <br />\n英國人基本上見你係油站有遲疑，都好樂意過來幫你。大家入完油之後記住自己油槍位置及讀數就可以，之後去reception俾錢就可以。<br />\n<br />\n最後，大家最好準備好offline嘅google map,因為未必每個地方都接收良好，呢個係小弟今次嘅經驗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2PQeYz5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2PQeYz5.png&h=00ed9e67&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MVmJRU6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMVmJRU6.png&h=3393f7fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DZ3cLe7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDZ3cLe7.png&h=f418f817&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/76X1Dz8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F76X1Dz8.png&h=36c37e37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泊車<br />\n<br />\n大家自駕嘅時候，難免要泊車。<br />\n首先，大家要留意自己住嘅酒店有冇提供泊車服務，基本比較偏僻嘅地方都會有免費泊車服務。如果係市中心嘅地方，則可能要去公共泊車嘅地方。<br />\n<br />\n英國泊車咪錶有幾鐘，有部份係短時間嘅例如一兩個小時，呢類咪錶係比較貴，例如在Oxford Castle附近嘅，都係要2-3磅一小時<br />\n<br />\n另外有一些係公共停車場，都係入錶，不過時間較長例如係每四小時或每廿四小時收費，此類會比較便宜。而且此類咪錶都可以用apps去上網付款或延長時間，非常方便。<br />\n<br />\n不過大家如果即場投幣咪錶，會有張receipt,請將佢放係車內擋風玻璃嘅左手邊，大多英國車輛都會有位俾大家攝紙仔。<br />\n<br />\n大家可以google睇，有好多英國自駕遊嘅網站。<br />\n大家都可以參考<br />\n<br />\n下篇開始講食<br />\n<br />\n待續"},{"pid":"f59890b4b6456c46457e2313f982181ce1236302","tid":938052,"uid":144369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T06:13:22.000Z","msg":"《紅葉》<br />\n<br />\n介紹食之前，介紹多兩個值得推薦嘅景點。<br />\n首先，當朋友知道小弟會自駕，推薦小弟去一個叫Westonbirt Aboretum 嘅公園。<br />\n由於小弟去嘅日子為十月初，正正係紅葉初開嘅日子，所以趁機會去左呢一個公園，公園大概離巴斯(Bath)20英里左右，如果開車，泊車免費。公園位處偏僻，非自駕者不太適宜。<br />\n<br />\n入場費為10磅。如果有時間，絕對為一個極佳hea嘅地方。當日我同太太係呢度留左2-3個小時，喜歡攝影嘅朋友不能錯過。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.forestryengland.uk/westonbirt/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forestryengland.uk%2Fwestonbirt%2F&d=cGeTo8mfJM0e0XC%2FG8%2BgJzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=b3dd7e2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.forestryengland.uk/westonbirt/</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟去時剛剛紅葉初開，未算盛開，如果盛開應該會好壯觀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NZNtpiW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNZNtpiW.png&h=5f1742c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nNG9Tcj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnNG9Tcj.png&h=abe8f7b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E8kraY3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE8kraY3.png&h=a45bf4d1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EAOgycq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEAOgycq.png&h=b9724473&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JxWFfqO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJxWFfqO.png&h=e6d82d8a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yh6ejSy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYh6ejSy.png&h=111c4b07&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VpmRm5W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVpmRm5W.png&h=c46db9e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果每年9月尾到十一月中有機會去英國嘅朋友，可以趁機一去。<br />\n<br />\n待續"},{"pid":"d30f3bc88ce4aa4e5177cec00466a40885135649","tid":938052,"uid":144369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T02:48:15.000Z","msg":"《Castle Combe》<br />\n<br />\n呢度係英國之旅個人來講最喜愛嘅地方， Castle Combe係一個好細嘅小鎮，小鎮居民應該100戶都冇，最出名為電影 War Horse嘅主拍攝場地，地方位於Bath附近，由巴斯（Bath)開車去大概為15英里左右，不過該處頗為偏僻，連入口都係單線雙程行車，所以請小心駕駛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/di9v0ua.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdi9v0ua.png&h=65a55ce0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aXXhFuc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaXXhFuc.png&h=cdec3b2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SFwBV2z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSFwBV2z.png&h=398a47a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wDXaf2B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwDXaf2B.png&h=c61e6287&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TgVfr9i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTgVfr9i.png&h=b1a91f6d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7YKcunF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7YKcunF.png&h=8bd3536c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家不是自駕，絕對不建議去呢個地方，因為太偏僻，又冇公共交通到達。不過如有自駕嘅朋友，呢度係一個值得推介嘅地方。<br />\n<br />\nCastle Combe彷似一個與世隔絕嘅小鎮，果一種寧靜悠閒嘅感覺絕對係香港冇可能感受得到，有機會一定要置身其中。<br />\n<br />\nCastle Combe有一間頗有名嘅酒店叫The Manor House,之前見有blogger介紹過，有興趣嘅朋友可以了解一下。<br />\n<br />\n待續"}]}